%tr
  %td.wrapper{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 20px;"}
    %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border-collapse: separate; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; width: 100%;"}
      %tr
        %td{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: top;"}
          %h2{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 15px;"}
            Forgot your password? No problem!

          %p{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; margin-top:25px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 30px;" }
            You can set a new one now! Click the link below.

          %p{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #759637; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width:180px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px"}
            = link_to edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), target: "_blank", style: "text-decoration: none; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 120%;" do
              Change my password

          %p{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; margin-top:35px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 30px;" }
            This link will expire after six hours. If you need a new one, you can request another on our #{link_to 'Log In page', new_user_session_url, style: 'font-size: 16px; color: #29159b'}.

          %p{:style => "font-family: sans-serif; margin-top:35px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 30px;" }
            If you didn't request a password reset you can delete this email.
